BT /F1 9 Tf 1 0 0 1 66.00 742.00 Tm (- The role rubric gives the classification step a conservative standard. It defines) Tj ET
BT /F1 9 Tf 1 0 0 1 66.00 730.00 Tm (  what counts as a confirmed school meal-program lead and what remains ambiguous.) Tj ET
BT /F1 9 Tf 1 0 0 1 66.00 715.00 Tm (- Ambiguity is not a failure of the workflow. It is part of the research record when) Tj ET
BT /F1 9 Tf 1 0 0 1 66.00 703.00 Tm (  the evidence is weak, vague, prospective, or unclear.) Tj ET
BT /F2 9 Tf 1 0 0 1 66.00 688.00 Tm (Transition: Now we know what the files contain and what our classification rules) Tj ET
BT /F2 9 Tf 1 0 0 1 66.00 675.00 Tm (are. Next we apply those rules row by row.) Tj ET
BT /F2 12 Tf 1 0 0 1 54.00 652.00 Tm (Module 4: Reviewer-Style Classification) Tj ET
BT /F1 9 Tf 1 0 0 1 66.00 635.00 Tm (- This module shows how the agent can help with judgment-heavy classification without) Tj ET
BT /F1 9 Tf 1 0 0 1 66.00 623.00 Tm (  making the judgment disappear.) Tj ET
BT /F1 9 Tf 1 0 0 1 66.00 608.00 Tm (- The school-lead perspective looks for strong positive evidence that a school) Tj ET
BT /F1 9 Tf 1 0 0 1 66.00 596.00 Tm (  cafeteria team or meal-program team led the modernization effort.) Tj ET
BT /F1 9 Tf 1 0 0 1 66.00 581.00 Tm (- The non-lead perspective protects the analysis from overcounting. Vendors, district) Tj ET
BT /F1 9 Tf 1 0 0 1 66.00 569.00 Tm (  offices, consultants, suppliers, and education partners may be important, but they) Tj ET
BT /F1 9 Tf 1 0 0 1 66.00 557.00 Tm (  are not automatically school leads.) Tj ET
BT /F1 9 Tf 1 0 0 1 66.00 542.00 Tm (- The ambiguity perspective keeps weak or undocumented evidence out of the confirmed) Tj ET
BT /F1 9 Tf 1 0 0 1 66.00 530.00 Tm (  category. That matters because one generous classification can turn into a) Tj ET
BT /F1 9 Tf 1 0 0 1 66.00 518.00 Tm (  misleading analysis variable.) Tj ET
BT /F1 9 Tf 1 0 0 1 66.00 503.00 Tm (- The reconciliation step turns several perspectives into one classification file and) Tj ET
BT /F1 9 Tf 1 0 0 1 66.00 491.00 Tm (  one audit note. The CSV carries the category, and the audit carries the reasoning.) Tj ET
BT /F1 9 Tf 1 0 0 1 66.00 476.00 Tm (- The classification file is useful because it is auditable. The human can see which) Tj ET
BT /F1 9 Tf 1 0 0 1 66.00 464.00 Tm (  rows were confirmed, which stayed ambiguous, and which cases still need review.) Tj ET
BT /F2 9 Tf 1 0 0 1 66.00 449.00 Tm (Transition: Now we have a classification file that can feed the panel, but only) Tj ET
BT /F2 9 Tf 1 0 0 1 66.00 436.00 Tm (confirmed lead rows affect the lead indicator.) Tj ET
BT /F2 12 Tf 1 0 0 1 54.00 413.00 Tm (Module 5: Build A School-Year Panel) Tj ET
BT /F1 9 Tf 1 0 0 1 66.00 396.00 Tm (- This module turns the inspected source files and the classification work into the) Tj ET
BT /F1 9 Tf 1 0 0 1 66.00 384.00 Tm (  main analysis-ready dataset.) Tj ET
BT /F1 9 Tf 1 0 0 1 66.00 369.00 Tm (- The panel has one row per school-year from 2019 through 2024. The important build) Tj ET
BT /F1 9 Tf 1 0 0 1 66.00 357.00 Tm (  rules are the unit of observation, the year range, crosswalk-based matching, grant) Tj ET
BT /F1 9 Tf 1 0 0 1 66.00 345.00 Tm (  timing, and conservative lead status.) Tj ET
BT /F1 9 Tf 1 0 0 1 66.00 330.00 Tm (- The workflow has a simple rhythm: rules first, script second, run third, inspect) Tj ET
BT /F1 9 Tf 1 0 0 1 66.00 318.00 Tm (  fourth. That rhythm keeps the code tied to the research choices instead of hiding) Tj ET
BT /F1 9 Tf 1 0 0 1 66.00 306.00 Tm (  them.) Tj ET
BT /F1 9 Tf 1 0 0 1 66.00 291.00 Tm (- The panel builder creates both a CSV and an audit note because the construction) Tj ET
BT /F1 9 Tf 1 0 0 1 66.00 279.00 Tm (  choices matter. Row counts, years, duplicate keys, unmatched names, and timing) Tj ET
BT /F1 9 Tf 1 0 0 1 66.00 267.00 Tm (  checks all belong in the record.) Tj ET
BT /F1 9 Tf 1 0 0 1 66.00 252.00 Tm (- The grant variables turn on in the award year, while grant amount is zero when no) Tj ET
BT /F1 9 Tf 1 0 0 1 66.00 240.00 Tm (  award occurred. The timing rule is what keeps the panel from blurring before and) Tj ET
BT /F1 9 Tf 1 0 0 1 66.00 228.00 Tm (  after.) Tj ET
BT /F1 9 Tf 1 0 0 1 66.00 213.00 Tm (- MealProgramLead turns on only after confirmed school-lead evidence. Ambiguous and) Tj ET
BT /F1 9 Tf 1 0 0 1 66.00 201.00 Tm (  non-lead partner rows stay excluded from that indicator.) Tj ET
BT /F2 9 Tf 1 0 0 1 66.00 186.00 Tm (Transition: Now we have the baseline panel, but the deliverable is not complete) Tj ET
BT /F2 9 Tf 1 0 0 1 66.00 173.00 Tm (until we explain what it can and cannot support.) Tj ET
BT /F1 8 Tf 1 0 0 1 54.00 28.00 Tm (Page 2 of 3) Tj ET
endstream
endobj
